## 3. Database & Data Engineering — 10 pts

| Criterion | Excellent (9–10) | Good (7–8) | Adequate (5–6) | Poor (0–4) |
|-----------|------------------|------------|-----------------|------------|
| **Gallery completeness** | ≥ 10 images per person for **all** team members + ≥ 2 additional individuals; varied poses, lighting, and expressions. | ≥ 10 images per person for all team members; limited variation. | < 10 images for some members; minimal diversity. | Gallery incomplete or poorly organized. |
| **Pre-processing pipeline** | Face alignment (5-point or 3D-based), normalization, and augmentation documented; pipeline is scripted and reproducible. | Alignment and resize applied; partially scripted. | Manual or ad-hoc cropping only. | No pre-processing. |

